      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver holds a documented quality management record with version control and regression testing covering the turbulence and scalar-transport modules used in this analysis.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R2 is used under an ISO-9001-certified QMS. Version-controlled input decks, regression test suite results, and change logs are archived in the project requirements document repository. Achieved level 2 satisfies MRL 2 threshold."
