      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method-of-manufactured-solutions (MMS) verification demonstrates second-order spatial accuracy for the momentum and scalar hemolysis transport equations.",
      "rationale": "MMS study conducted on canonical rotating-disk geometry confirms observed order of accuracy p = 1.97 ± 0.05, consistent with the second-order finite-volume discretisation. Results archived in validation result https://uofa.net/morrison/validation/solver-verification-mms-2024."
