      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study (3.2 M, 8.7 M, 22.1 M cells) yields GCI = 3.1% for RH at the worst-case operating point (6 LPM, 3000 RPM). Production mesh is 8.7 M cells, balancing accuracy and computational cost per project requirements."
    },
