      "rationale": "CFD-predicted RH deviates from experimental mean by −4% to +11% across the 5-point operating map. All predictions satisfy the ±15% acceptance criterion. Detailed comparison tabulated in validation result https://uofa.net/morrison/validation/pump-hemolysis-bench-2024."
